name: Queen Ansurek
description: After a revelation of traitors in her court, Queen Ansurek decides she must eradicate the palace's invaders herself. However, paranoia over whom she can trust gnaws at her psyche. With her allies dwindling, Queen Ansurek may delve into dark powers to attain victory, even if that means her most loyal soldiers become her next meal...

item.name: Formula: Enchant Weapon - Authority of the Depths

sections.title: Damage Dealers
sections.body_text:
$bullet;Devoted Worshippers cast Hspell:448458[Cosmic Apocalypse] if not defeated.
$bullet;Hspell:445877[Froth Vapor] occurs if Hspell:445422[Frothing Gluttony] absorbs Hspell:444829[Queen's Summons].
$bullet;Hspell:437417[Venom Nova] inflicts significant harm unless avoided with Hspell:438846[Reactive Froth].
$bullet;Hspell:445422[Frothing Gluttony] inflicts significant harm unless avoided with Hspell:443915[Abyssal Conduit].

sections.title: Stage One: A Queen's Venom
sections.body_text: Ansurek battles with poison and web to show her mastery of traditional Nerubian power.

sections.title: Intermission: The Spider's Web
sections.body_text: Ansurek shrouds herself in webbing and feeds on her weakened enemies.

sections.title: Stage Two: Royal Ascension
sections.body_text: Ansurek calls reinforcements to her aid as she ascends to her private chamber.

sections.title: Caustic Skitterer
sections.body_text: Caustic Skitterers land and attack nearby players.

sections.title: Stage Three: Paranoia's Feast
sections.body_text: Ansurek embraces a dark power as paranoia takes hold.
